# Summary

This project demonstrates a complete and reproducible AI pipeline that integrates transcription, translation, alignment, and speaker-aware speech generation into a single system.

The pipeline focuses on segment-level processing and speaker-conditioned synthesis to preserve timing and speaker structure, while maintaining reliability and reproducibility through Docker deployment.
